Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:15.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you're right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:17.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hecklers will heckle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:18.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:21.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't pry into the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:23.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can just practice during your free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.56,0:03:27.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll still be free on weeknights\Nand afternoons on the weekend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:30.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess I should think about my work schedule, too.{This sounds like Momoka's trying to map her schedule with Nina's schedule for band practice, but *maybe* she's referring to Nina getting a job like she mentioned in ep 1...}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:32.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Starting a band?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:38.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said you would!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:39.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:43.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did! "Please flip 'em off with me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:46.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do something about your finger-flipping habit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:48.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:50.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That didn't mean I was gonna be a singer,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:52.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but that we all have our own roles to fill.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm here to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're here to play music.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.26,0:03:58.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh. That's what it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew something was off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You surprised me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:08.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It gets this crowded at this hour, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ooh, something an out-of-towner would say!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:11.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:15.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, putting your all in studying is fine and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but don't you want to try being in a band once?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:20.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:23.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not asking you to play an instrument.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think you'd be a good vocalist, personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vocalist?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have a nice voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and what's more, you have the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:41.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bands are where people {who've piled up things they want to get off their chest}with pent up feelings gather, in my opinion.{バンドってさ、言いたいことが溜まりに溜まってるやつが集まってやるものだと思うんだよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:44.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like "I wanna fall in love!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or "I'm sick of this world!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:50.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or "That was so epic!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or "I love myself!", or "I hate myself!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:58.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you going to sing by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:00.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:03.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but being in a band sure is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you're with others, some'll talk smack,\Nthen others'll tattle, so things get awkward,{一緒にいると陰口あって告げ口あってギスギスして}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:09.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but bringing it up would ruin things so you hold it in,{言ったら負けだ！って我慢するけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but since you're always together, it all builds up{いつも一緒だからどんどん溜まって}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then you get tired of being in the same room{同じ空気を吸うにもいやになって}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and finally blow a fuse—{ついに爆発して}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You haven't said a single positive thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:19.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever. It's just fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:26.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can create things as a group that you couldn't do alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:28.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:30.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:34.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is probably the closest station to your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:38.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This area doesn't really have city-like vibes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:40.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:42.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your place is over that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:44.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but let me show you the grocery store this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:46.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:53.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.\NI'm the older one here, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:54.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think of it as paying for my stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:56.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:59.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you put the rest in the fridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Warning you though, I'm not that amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:04.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you do know how to cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I kind of like cooking, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:08.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm, where's the knife...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:12.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a bit like writing songs, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You chop the ingredients\Nwhile you wait for the water to boil,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.61,0:06:18.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then prep the sauce\Nwhile the ingredients are stewing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You progress on multiple things in parallel,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:24.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then combine their results all into one in the end.{哲学だもんな}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:25.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:27.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ugh! This knife isn't cutting it.{は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for not having a better knife....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.87,0:06:32.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not something you need to apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just that I haven't been able\Nto take care of anything....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:38.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though I chose to live by myself....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think that's funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah. I just remembered I was like this, once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:47.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just have to face it head on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:50.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"What do I do?", "I messed up!", "That's how it works?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just have to learn by trial and error.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:56.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like realising you don't have plates to put this on.{could use an edit...}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:00.57,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\frz5.4\c&H000000&\be1\fs43\pos(1094,198)}Things I need to buy!!\N• Plates\N• Ladle\N• Tension rod\N• Colander
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:06:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:00.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:04.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should buy a light soon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do we just eat out of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:10.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nina, you sure you're not from a posh family?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's something a rich girl would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:15.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? No, you've got it all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My family's as typical as they get.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:20.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Except, they're just a little unique...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:22.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have house rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,House rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, like laws to follow at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:34.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,1. Always eat dinner at the table with all family members present.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:38.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,2. No smartphone usage in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,3. A family meeting is to be held every Sunday evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:47.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:52.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And some parents were amazed that\Nthere was a family doing that sort of thing,{tbh my interpretation here is probably off but parents meeting one another at the same school happens afaik which trickles down to their children...is the implication I'm getting here...but it's 親にあって being said and not 親がいて so w/e I wish I had a TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:54.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So word about us got around at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:08:02.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then I stopped attending class\Nand eventually dropped out....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:06.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who cares why I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:10.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:14.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's written all over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:18.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The most popular girl at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:19.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:22.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she hops from one hottie to the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:25.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Did you get bullied by her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:26.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:32.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would I know? Something about me\Nmust have hit a nerve or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't try to get back at her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:40.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Girls like her build up a support network so that\Nyou can't retaliate before they start messing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:42.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They get everyone to give you the silent treatment,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:46.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and at one point I even got hurt enough that I needed to be taken to the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:50.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but school, and even my family,\Nsaid not to make a big deal about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:51.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hotpot's gonna get overcooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:56.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's fine. I like veggies soggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:09:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really should become a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could probably write five songs\Nout of those topics just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:08.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've wanted to experience being in a band\Nwhere I'm not the vocalist at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See what it's like to only focus on playing the guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:13.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:15.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:21.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dropping outta high school
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:24.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,means y'got fewer future prospects.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be too late for regrets\Nwhen ya figure out what ya wanna do in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then going to university should be enough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:36.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As long as I study and get into university on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:38.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I remain a high school dropout
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:43.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and don't ever attend university, it's all over for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All over, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:47.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I didn't mean it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just that at this rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it'll feel like I've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:56.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll have lost to the bullies, my parents, and my teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:58.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:02.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was some more beer in the fridge, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:14.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:16.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That one has books.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:20.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take the heavy ones,\Nso grab the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.06,0:10:21.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will one trip be enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the last big item, so I think it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you go double check the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:28.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.57,0:10:33.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not forgetting anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really need to study....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:41.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:43.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This'll still be useful to you, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:45.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:49.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like I can play it, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:54.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I should take it back from you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:58.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:01.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sure you don't want me to come with?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.48,0:11:06.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I ask for one last favour?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:13.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.62,0:11:20.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know there was a place like this around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:23.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've probably heard about the Tama River before, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:25.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a lot wider than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't think Tokyo had a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:30.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokyo's beyond that bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:32.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were this close to making it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:34.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was really just a hair's breadth away....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:37.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any requests?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:39.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:42.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to hear your voice one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sing whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:48.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And good luck on your studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:51.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just moving back to the same unit\NI dragged you to a while back,{really gotta wonder about her roommate tho}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:54.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so let's go out to eat again when you're free.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:56.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:59.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give it your all with your music, too, Momoka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best to write more songs\Nyou'll fall head over heels for again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:09.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give'em the finger and blow them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.21,0:12:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whenever you feel like flipping someone off,\Ntry using your pinky instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:20.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.19,0:12:31.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:36.19,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,If you found yourself inside my shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:39.49,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,How would you decide which path to ignore?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:44.12,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,All the blank white pages that are set before me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:47.45,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,Full of simple questions anyone could answer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:49.37,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,It's form over function
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:53.75,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,But my fingers are trembling anxiously
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:55.46,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,There's no right answer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:57.05,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,No one wins or loses
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:58.67,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,And it's all so simple
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:00.34,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,I can only march on
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:02.30,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,And carve out my own path
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.97,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,No more brooding
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:08.48,Insert - Void,,0,0,0,,If I keep on debating, I'll waste my life
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:16.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:20.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"'You can't give up,' said Jim."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:25.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"'The light of hope'"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:27.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"'will surely shine in the darkness.'"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:36.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still need to go shopping.
