Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:54.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Can I come over to pick it up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you buy a light yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:48.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone gave me one I'm not gonna use today, want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you! Yes, I'll take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good evening...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:04.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:08.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:10.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:13.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! You got here quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:17.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about the short notice.{technically momoka's the one who brought up the lamp so maybe there's a better phrase to use here than short notice...}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The light I was talking about is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like it should do the trick, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine as long as it turns on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:27.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sup? Have you gotten used to things here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:30.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good question....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:34.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you're here, how about we go to dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:35.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm working again, so I'll treat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:38.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure! I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:41.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So she's Nina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:43.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Awa-san. She gave me that light.\NShe's joining me as a drummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Subaru Awa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.85,0:15:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm Iseri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:55.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're joining us for dinner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:56.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not treating you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:58.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You're lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have the money for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.90,0:16:01.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:06.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm gonna head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Join us! Nina only turned up in Tokyo a bit ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Subaru's the same age as you, y'know.{speech slightly goes after keyframe, probably fine?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:17.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is more like hotpot than shabu-shabu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:19.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You added way too many veggies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:24.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cabbage, if stewed for too long,\Nloses its texture and tastes nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:25.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:27.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:28.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What music are you into, by the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.85,0:16:32.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:34.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any bands or Vocaloid artists you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I recall correctly, she's into\NShowa era music because of her grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.77,0:16:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? That sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I listen to that sometimes.\NWhich artists do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:47.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, I wouldn't say I'm that into—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:48.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this GureRuchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoa, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.41,0:16:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You listen to GureRuchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I've been to one of their concerts?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:55.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And again at a music festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.87,0:16:58.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Music festival? The one in Chiba last year?{is that a rickroll intro}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:16:59.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:01.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were a total mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:03.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mess, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:06.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would definitely keep them off future guest line-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.26,0:17:09.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They haven't held a proper concert since.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:11.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh. I never noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.89,0:17:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I think you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:16.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their debut was pretty good, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you go to concerts or other events, Nina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:20.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not really....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:21.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:23.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pot's kinda getting lonely,\Nwanna drop some meat in?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:25.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, do you not like meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:26.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:30.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:37.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No chemistry?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:39.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then try talking to her a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:44.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's trying pretty hard to find common ground.{接点も通って頑張ってるんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:46.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:49.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is she forcing herself to talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:52.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course. Everyone starts off like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:54.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't know anything about each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She sounds so pretentious. It pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're overthinking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She mentioned going to a drama school,\Nso that's kind of normal for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She doesn't mean any harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:08.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sure are friendly, aren't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're totally screaming, "Look at me,"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.53,0:18:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"humouring a miserable girl like her."\Nin that head of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:15.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with the pessimism?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:17.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not being pessimistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you judge people with that mindset
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:21.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you'll never be able to talk with anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:28.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:30.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:34.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt I'll ever get along with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:36.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't help it, I have a shit personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:37.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now look here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:39.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll forever be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.27,0:18:41.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for treating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:50.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're...welcome?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, what a doofus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She doesn't even realise she has what she most needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What {\i1}am{\i0} I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:17.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though she reached out to me....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:20.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though she was thinking about my circumstances....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm an idiot, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:28.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm stupid as heck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:32.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the dumbest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,God! Damn! Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm such an idiot....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:41.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:42.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No you shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:43.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whassat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:47.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:50.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:53.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Quit that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:56.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:20:00.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut yer trap!{wtf, suddenly kyushu-ben (according to jisho at least, maybe it's also kumamoto-ben...)?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:33.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't even plug in the light by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:37.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll spend my entire life in darkness....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:40.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be in the dumps forever....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:43.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dumps....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:48.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's start a band after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:49.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.40,0:20:51.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:53.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Subaru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:56.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should pick a better place to hide your spare key.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And wow, the light's already this tattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.41,0:21:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I said, I love your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would you lie to me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:11.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:14.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You over-complicate and convolute things,{ehhhh}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but that's because you can't lie to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so frail, but you'd rather die than change your tune.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:26.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You remind me{それはさ、私が忘れていた私が大好きでいつまでも抱きしめてみたい私の歌なんだ。} of what I'd once forgotten—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:30.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a song of mine so dear to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.48,0:21:33.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wish I could hold onto it forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't...I don't need to hear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:52.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you laughing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.46,0:21:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:21:57.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.59,0:22:03.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just shove all that pain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.76,0:22:04.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,into your songs!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.10,0:22:06.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:21.95,EDStyle,,0,0,0,,Never influenced by anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.95,0:22:23.74,EDStyle,,0,0,0,,Never becoming anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.74,0:22:26.62,EDStyle,,0,0,0,,I laughed, thinking it a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.03,0:22:29.83,EDStyle,,0,0,0,,Numbed by the weakness I had forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.16,0:22:33.04,EDStyle,,0,0,0,,I can't even say that I'm lonely
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.04,0:22:36.21,EDStyle,,0,0,0,,This fragile heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.21,0:22:38.59,EDStyle,,0,0,0,,Vulnerable to even casual conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.63,0:22:44.76,EDStyle,,0,0,0,,Is incapable of making anyone happy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.97,0:22:52.14,EDStyle,,0,0,0,,But still, I feel a growing hope
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.14,0:22:57.98,EDStyle,,0,0,0,,Moving past all of the lies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:23:01.40,EDStyle,,0,0,0,,I just want to hear that I'm not wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:04.57,EDStyle,,0,0,0,,I'm a dreamer, I'm young
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:08.20,EDStyle,,0,0,0,,I don't care if I'm still the same today
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:10.74,EDStyle,,0,0,0,,I just want to sing with you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.74,0:23:14.21,EDStyle,,0,0,0,,My emotions stir so often
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.21,0:23:17.38,EDStyle,,0,0,0,,I've been hated
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.38,0:23:20.63,EDStyle,,0,0,0,,But I'm going to keep on walking
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.63,0:23:26.84,EDStyle,,0,0,0,,Proud of myself who can never become anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.39,0:23:30.18,EDStyle,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:33.39,EDStyle,,0,0,0,,I believe in myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:40.61,EDStyle,,0,0,0,,Every time I get hurt, I just need to sing
